469fb9ad-ac33-4765-bcba-66b4ded30dee.title: Dominic Onion
469fb9ad-ac33-4765-bcba-66b4ded30dee.text:
Welcome to the Nightmare Zone!
Would you like me to create a dream for you?

options.text: Can you tell me about the dreams?

915fa8ab-8c80-4c2d-ac08-6f8a5e09995f.title: Dominic Onion
915fa8ab-8c80-4c2d-ac08-6f8a5e09995f.text:
My name's Dominic Onion but you can call me Dom,
or Mr Onion.

9112558d-5b70-4521-b6fa-54bae74855df.title: <player>
9112558d-5b70-4521-b6fa-54bae74855df.text: Mr Oni...Dom, how did you get that name?

965730c7-305c-4ae7-81d3-a40a5030538a.title: Dominic Onion
965730c7-305c-4ae7-81d3-a40a5030538a.text:
Well that's a long story...but I can tell you that it
involved my parents, 3 blurberry specials, and a
chinchompa.

8eec2441-1194-42b7-bc97-08896b6b4e77.title: Dominic Onion
8eec2441-1194-42b7-bc97-08896b6b4e77.text:
Oh yes, Nigel played a crucial role in the whole debacle.
It's all very amusing now that I think back to it.

9fb89b68-db68-4d57-a9e1-d24198af52d6.title: Dominic Onion
9fb89b68-db68-4d57-a9e1-d24198af52d6.text:
Don't worry, it's not as bad as it sounds...most of the
time.

65d52b5a-f9d2-4d34-a96b-8907817aeed4.title: Dominic Onion
65d52b5a-f9d2-4d34-a96b-8907817aeed4.text:
Truth be told, that name wasn't my first choice, it's
what the local folk have been calling it and so it sort of
stuck.

3c5d3eb2-111d-4373-ab51-8eedf8926d25.title: Dominic Onion
3c5d3eb2-111d-4373-ab51-8eedf8926d25.text:
My original plan came to me in a vivid dream when I
was younger you see, I saw myself running a
successful business from a great structure in a strange
land.

2875a7c7-cf3e-41c7-9596-ecf64ee59a2e.title: Dominic Onion
2875a7c7-cf3e-41c7-9596-ecf64ee59a2e.text:
Well, I say strange, but I'd never left Lunar Isle at
the time and this place was very hot and dry, unlike
anything I'd seen before.

bfa1fb89-6587-4176-bde4-9f1361918f9d.title: Dominic Onion
bfa1fb89-6587-4176-bde4-9f1361918f9d.text:
When I told my father about the dream he laughed and
said I should become a banker like him and his father
before him but in that moment I knew that it wasn't the
life for me.

6a8c454c-d271-40b0-9a9b-3615ac3c9b9b.title: Dominic Onion
6a8c454c-d271-40b0-9a9b-3615ac3c9b9b.text:
I had to find out what this dream meant and if it was a
vision of the future or not.

b4c33aa9-0038-4f9a-94cb-37a3741a6233.title: Dominic Onion
b4c33aa9-0038-4f9a-94cb-37a3741a6233.text:
Growing up, I studied hard to find out more about
magic, especially oneiromancy and the interpretation of
dreams.

9cba36ea-285b-41f3-89d1-71bc39c5292f.title: Dominic Onion
9cba36ea-285b-41f3-89d1-71bc39c5292f.text:
Having learned as much as I could on Lunar Isle I set
out to find and learn from other great wizards I'd
heard of in stories as a child.

cea6d3cf-fabb-4fe4-b060-10db07dbeb9c.title: Dominic Onion
cea6d3cf-fabb-4fe4-b060-10db07dbeb9c.text:
I set off to travel the world, discovering more about
dreams to enable me to understand the dream I'd had
as a child.

1c0cec4f-a037-4cb9-ac76-c7a358636778.title: Dominic Onion
1c0cec4f-a037-4cb9-ac76-c7a358636778.text:
I needed to know what this dream meant and if it was
truly a vision of the future.

f1ec6f1f-a281-4b0c-ab88-848cbe65d760.title: Dominic Onion
f1ec6f1f-a281-4b0c-ab88-848cbe65d760.text:
If so I knew I had to try and find this location and
build the huge tower I saw.

a2ce7c09-cc34-4e17-b7ea-7d783a91cf62.title: Dominic Onion
a2ce7c09-cc34-4e17-b7ea-7d783a91cf62.text:
I was going to call it 'Dom Onion's Tower', but I've
not found this strange place or gathered enough money
to build it just yet.

6e735298-5a6d-4abe-9cea-428e90c9d85c.title: Dominic Onion
6e735298-5a6d-4abe-9cea-428e90c9d85c.text:
That's why I've setup this small business venture in the
mean time selling dreams to people. I just need a big
enough crowd to kickstart my business.

16bc20fe-9532-453b-a451-9febd5546446.title: Dominic Onion
16bc20fe-9532-453b-a451-9febd5546446.text:
It's all part of my five year plan, and who knows,
perhaps my dream will come true; I'll discover this place
and build Dom Onion's Tower!

46636db7-4249-4119-9384-60da4cedbd6d.title: <player>
46636db7-4249-4119-9384-60da4cedbd6d.text: Can you tell me about the dreams?

4a1f5fec-d971-4077-b7fa-fae7ad03d070.title: Dominic Onion
4a1f5fec-d971-4077-b7fa-fae7ad03d070.text:
Certainly. I can delve into your memories and search
for the key events that have affected you on your
adventures.

088b4b32-3ede-4a33-a44e-4fae7a050c37.title: Dominic Onion
088b4b32-3ede-4a33-a44e-4fae7a050c37.text:
I then take the essence of these memories and put that
in the vial you see on the plinth.

fc34e5c1-324d-452c-9982-a4c473deb3ee.title: Dominic Onion
fc34e5c1-324d-452c-9982-a4c473deb3ee.text:
I imbue a bit of magic, then give the vial a bit of a
shake, and when you drink it you'll be able to re-live an
encounter close to the original.

4864aa12-820e-43d1-9a54-19159141a0fc.title: Dominic Onion
4864aa12-820e-43d1-9a54-19159141a0fc.text:
Don't worry though, when you're in a dream, you're
perfectly safe even if it does seem very real.

4b5159e8-fd83-4166-8b5b-f95339515277.title: Dominic Onion
4b5159e8-fd83-4166-8b5b-f95339515277.text:
If you sucessfully overcome the dream or die trying,
you'll leave the dream state and return to normal with
your grey matter and appendages intact.

20033107-bf32-42c7-b879-3115c25c3580.title: <player>
20033107-bf32-42c7-b879-3115c25c3580.text: Are all dreams the same or are there different options?

668920b7-d6e1-4400-9ad5-6bd2025f0e40.title: Dominic Onion
668920b7-d6e1-4400-9ad5-6bd2025f0e40.text:
Oh no, they can vary wildly! You can choose from one
of three main options.

0e579073-e945-4483-b21e-7c0e2505b224.title: Dominic Onion
0e579073-e945-4483-b21e-7c0e2505b224.text:
Firstly, I can create a one-on-one encounter with an
adversary you've defeated in your adventures. People
like to practice in these dreams.

9d00fc43-5efa-488a-9c0c-5ea0e9195f88.title: Dominic Onion
9d00fc43-5efa-488a-9c0c-5ea0e9195f88.text:
Then there's a sort of Endurance dream, where you
face enemies in encounter after encounter, and try to
survive to the end.

0e6587d3-1826-4e05-ade6-b47b311556cc.title: Dominic Onion
0e6587d3-1826-4e05-ade6-b47b311556cc.text:
And finally there's something I like to call a Rumble,
where you face multiple adversaries at the same time. I
imbue a bit more magic and shake the vial harder to
create that one!

cf2c2764-5b3d-4124-a6ef-f9fecfa5f1b8.title: Dominic Onion
cf2c2764-5b3d-4124-a6ef-f9fecfa5f1b8.text:
You can invite friends to fight alongside you in a
Rumble dream. Once I've set up the dream for you,
step into the enclosure and invite up to 4 friends.

d166ab36-fe3c-4e22-9d7e-98e457541f7e.title: Dominic Onion
d166ab36-fe3c-4e22-9d7e-98e457541f7e.text:
For the Endurance and Rumble dreams, I charge a
fee for my work. I don't like handling the money
directly, so instead I've set up a secure coffer.

e55b6136-11e6-432e-a2d5-6dc04d6afa9e.title: Dominic Onion
e55b6136-11e6-432e-a2d5-6dc04d6afa9e.text:
After you've asked me to set up a dream, put some
money in my coffer. I'll deduct the fee from the coffer
when you start the dream.

15e14485-ac72-4509-bbaa-cef9578356c4.title: Dominic Onion
15e14485-ac72-4509-bbaa-cef9578356c4.text:
There's a red vial on the other plinth. Your friends can
drink from it to enter your dream as a spectator to
observe your progress.

695ee596-7553-49a7-ac46-7a8829cc808e.title: Dominic Onion
695ee596-7553-49a7-ac46-7a8829cc808e.text:
Finally here's one other option you get, and that's how
difficult the encounters are. As well as the normal
dreams, the bravest adventurers can choose a harder
version*.

a4203c01-156c-4397-a69e-b0abb0f6710e.text:
*Terms and conditions apply: Mr Onion, henceforth known as Dom,
cannot be held liable for accidental loss of limbs (yours or otherwise)
and or psychological damage as a result of entering the Nightmare
Zone. Please note there is a strict no-refunds policy, and all dream
purchases are final.

1df87ae0-d3ea-4797-b863-cffa48bdcd1b.title: Dominic Onion
1df87ae0-d3ea-4797-b863-cffa48bdcd1b.text:
Certainly. You can practice for free, but the larger
dreams require more skill to imbue the potions and so
there's a fee for those.
